yingyinNormal.en: We should simply ask the enemy not to invade on a Sabbath cause Private Doss here is a prayer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们应要求敌人别在安息日进攻因为列兵多斯在此祈祷。

yingyinNormal.en: We've never made it past the first round of the scholastic decathlon. You could be our answered prayer.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我们从没通过第一轮的学校全能比赛,你是我们的希望。

yingyinNormal.en: Thank you all. After much reflection and prayer and returning to Scripture with an open heart, I realized that I was wrong.
yingyinNormal.zh: 谢谢各位，经过长久的沉思和祈祷并打开心灵，回归圣经我发现我错了。

yingyinNormal.en: To our service members who are away from home we say an extra prayer for you and your loved ones and we renew our commitment to take care of you as well as you've taken care of us.
yingyinNormal.zh: 对我们远离家乡的服役人员，我们要特别地为你们以及你们所爱的人们祈祷，我们重申我们关怀你们的承诺正如你们爱护我们一样。
